headline: TPM by S&P Global to Convene Shipping and Supply Chain Leaders in California, March 1-4
summary: The 26th annual TPM, S&P Global's premier shipping and supply chain conference organized by the Journal of Commerce, will bring together senior decision-makers from across the global logistics ecosystem March 1 – 4 in Long Beach, California.
